  nodes:
  - editorLabel: Garrett - Wraith Killed
    lines:
    - speaker: Garrett
      text: "The guards just got word. Whatever was causing the trouble \u2014 it's
        over. They're already talking about reopening the road."
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Garrett
      text: I don't know what you did out there, but the forest has calmed down overnight.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Garrett
      text: Also, did you know the old man by the campfire is gone? Just vanished.
        Strange timing, don't you think?
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    - speaker: Garrett
      text: ...Anyway. I owe you a blade. A good one. Come back when I've got proper
        materials again.
      portraitOverride: {fileID: 0}
      emote: 
      sfx: {fileID: 0}
      sfxVolume: 1
      autoAdvanceDelay: 0
      tags: []
    choices: []
